Day 89: Ansible Manage Services

Date: December 17, 2025
Overview
Controlled service states using Ansible.
Key Concepts Learned

Service module
Service state (started, stopped, restarted)
Enable on boot
Service handlers

Playbook
yaml- name: Ensure nginx is running
  service:
    name: nginx
    state: started
    enabled: yes

- name: Restart nginx if config changed
  service:
    name: nginx
    state: restarted

Challenges Faced
Understanding when to use handlers vs direct service tasks.
